      <div class="content-wrapper title">
                          <h1 class="title" id="page-title">The Hill&#039;s Campaign Report: Trump inflames red state-blue state coronavirus divide</h1>
                <div class="submitted-wrp">
    <span class="submitted-by">
    By Julia Manchester, Max Greenwood and Jonathan Easley - <span class="submitted-date">04/17/20 05:44 PM EDT</span>
  </span>
  <a href="/homenews/campaign/493387-the-hills-campaign-report-trump-inflames-red-state-blue-state-coronavirus#bottom-story-socials" class="disqus-comments" data-disqus-identifier="node/493387"></a>  </div>
      </div>
